Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:59.16,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}崩れゆく　こんな世界で　たったひとつ信じるのは　この心の痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:05.46,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}Black cross sorting With tears in force.
